these are the keybinds for my vxwm config. Not much more to it

the important stuff (except apps and moving):
mod + d --                   dmenu
mod + c --                   kill window
mod + b --                   set layout floating
mod + n --                   set layout tiling
mod + m --                   set layout stacking
mod + shift + q --           quit
alt + f --                   fullscreen
alt + c --                   center window
mod + ctrl + z --            pin window

movement:
mod + arrows --              move window
alt + ctrl + arrows --       resize window
mod + shift + arrows --      move view 
alt + arrows --              move to other window
mod + left click --          move when on canvas
mod + shift + left click --  move when on window

apps:
mod + q --                   urxvt
mod + f --                   helium
mod + e --                   dolphin
mod + s --                   kate

less important stuff:
mod + shift + s --           flameshot gui
mod + shift + a --           flameshot full
mod + shift + b --           toggle bar (only for the native vxwm bar)
alt + tab --                 goes through your windows
alt + shift + tab --         same but backwards
mod + tab --                 view all workspaces
mod + space --               switch between last 2 layouts
mod + shift + 0 --           tag (even idk??)
mod + y --                   focusmon (i honestly dont know)
mod + u --                   focusmon (same with this)
mod + shift + y --           tagmon (idk..)
mod + shift + u --           tagmon (stop interrogating me)
mod + r --                   center of the canvas

tiling:
mod + k --                   moves master window
mod + l --                   same but backwards
mod + i --                   sets master width
mod + o --                   same but backwards
mod + enter --               switches between masters
mod + plus --                increase gaps
mod + minus --               decrease gaps
mod + shift + plus --        set gaps to default
